parameters: Congratulations!\.\. You've reached the end of the \c[18]\i[531] Anzu Route\c[0] Demo!
Check the links in the Title Screen to play the full build of Down the Neko Hole!
Pinned down,\. the maid squirms and writhes before finally surrending to the feline superiority.
Almost asphyxiated,\. she manages a final wriggle,\. breaking free from Neneko's hold!
"Something" digs Kanako underground.\.\. Nothing squirms and writhes anymore in the room.
\n<\N[1]>Coward...\.\.\. I couldn't finish her!\.\. ...\.\.\. Just how far does this place go?
\n<\N[1]>What a pain!\.\. If that thing is still alive somewhere below us...\.\.\.
\n<\N[1]>I'd better go check on the blondie pervert...\.\.\. if she's still asleep I'll have to get her out of this place.
\n<Headmaid Kanako>Purr~\.\. Purr~\.\. Where are you,\. kitty~?
\n<\N[1]>!!\.\. Why are you singing...\.\.\. have you gone crazy?\.\.
\n<\N[1]>This place...\.\.\. everyone in this place is messed up in the head...
\n<Headmaid Kanako>Two little kittens,\. they lost their Mami~
\n<Headmaid Kanako>They began to cry,\. poor little kittens~
\n<\N[1]>What are you talking about...?\.\. Two little kittens...?\.\.
\n<Headmaid Kanako>Purr~\.\. Purr~\.\. You fell down the Hole,\. kitty~?
\n<Headmaid Kanako>Purr~\.\. Purr~\.\. Purr~\.\. Oh,\. let us have some of it~
Like a meat bag,\. the stitches on the maid's belly open,\. revealing the gaping horror which is Kanako.
\n<Headmaid Kanako>Oh,\. Mami dear,\. do you not hear...\.\.\. your kitten's crying,\. and you're not here~
\n<\N[1]>Alright,\. then!\.\. We're on!\.\. Noone drives me into a corner!!
